message.body: OK. She said she figured it out & one would be here tomorrow. Cindy said she can come on Monday.
Do you want to be there when she comes & if so what time works best for you? Morning? Midday? Afternoon? Evening?
OK. I'll let you know what time she is coming.
I don't need to be there but let me know when bc I've been locking my door
I've been ok in my room, but my bed is still isolated etc
NP. I was hoping to get her back out there a little sooner but it took Alex a little longer then I expected to get everything together.
Pls call me when you get a chance. Thanks.
